sentence: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Intel Corp ( INTC ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 2.4%.
Year to date, Intel Corp has lost about 17.5% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Travelers Companies ( TRV ), trading up 0.5%.
Travelers Companies is lower by about 5.5% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Procter & Gamble ( PG ), trading up 0.7%, and Nike ( NKE ), trading up 2.1% on the day.
